                            NIVEL DE ALERTA: ${riskText} (Score: ${riskScore}/10)
                        </div>
                        ${radar && radar.panoramaNota ? `<div class="panorama-banner"><strong>PANORAMA MENSUAL:</strong> ${radar.panoramaNota}</div>` : ''}

